          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "S2 still says `T001-T004` are in the same commit, but S1 already marks `T001` as done with commit hash `5c159af139735232dc538b54b8fd886c34702fc1`. That makes the Batch A grouping internally inconsistent: T001 is no longer part of the same implementation commit as T002-T004.",
